name: Angie Varona
description:
Angie Varona

It's Instagram Model season here at CivitAI apparently. 3.8M followers.

TBH I'm shocked no one has created a model out of this, uh, model. Maybe someone did and I missed it (sorry!) otherwise I was not going to let this injustice stand.

This is pre-pregnancy Angie by the way, I'm sure there's a LoRA out there that can fix that for you if you like that sort of thing.

I used a base model of SDv1.4, a learning rate of 4e-03 and this is the result after 4500 steps.

Do you like my work? Buy me a beer!
